	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">中国公司在和 AC 米兰谈收购，但成不成是另一回事</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-11 17:59:23 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">4</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">7</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

